      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Alvaro Cardoso</b>\n</p><p><b>Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</b>,<br />\na Portuguese <a href=\"/Checkers\" title=\"Checkers\">checkers</a> programmer, and author of the Portuguese checkers (Spanish checkers, classical checkers, Jogo de Damas Clássicas \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>) engine <i>Profound</i>, initially written in <a href=\"/Basic\" title=\"Basic\">Powerbasic 2.1</a> augmented with many <a href=\"/Assembly\" title=\"Assembly\">assembly</a> instructions <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, considered as one of the strongest classical checkers engines <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. Alvaro is long term member in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=152959\">Using just Upperbounds and Lowerbounds</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Bound\" title=\"Bound\">Bound</a>, <a href=\"/Upper_Bound\" title=\"Upper Bound\">Upper Bound</a>, <a href=\"/Lower_Bound\" title=\"Lower Bound\">Lower Bound</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=156310\">Iterative deepening deep increment</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=214125\">Non power of two hash table sizes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 18, 2002 <a href=\"/Hash_Table\" title=\"Hash Table\">Hash Table</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=285939\">ALL node definition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 21, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Node_Types\" title=\"Node Types\">Node Types</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=441449\">DTC EGTB algorithms needed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 12, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=445457\">History based pruning question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=446349\">Counter move heuristic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 30, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Countermove_Heuristic\" title=\"Countermove Heuristic\">Countermove Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6302&amp;p=29956\">Wu / Beal retrograde analisys algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 10, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Retrograde_Analysis\" title=\"Retrograde Analysis\">Retrograde Analysis</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=21754\">A simple book learning method</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 12, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Book_Learning\" title=\"Book Learning\">Book Learning</a>, <a href=\"/Persistent_Hash_Table\" title=\"Persistent Hash Table\">Persistent Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27017\">Extensions: everywhere or near the tips?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 15, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/deep-profound/1orssru9D30/WPKRPC2r_-oJ\">Re: questão do profound</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Groups\">Google Groups</a>, July 11, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=367283\">Extended Null-Move Reductions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Null Move Reductions\">Null Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43658\">File size for files &gt; 4Gb</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49388\">MEM_LARGE_PAGES</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 18, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">Memory</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49592\">Multithreaded LRU</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 06, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">Memory</a>, <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49719\">evaluating color agnostic terms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Asymmetric_Evaluation\" title=\"Asymmetric Evaluation\">Asymmetric Evaluation</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58758\">crafty eval cache</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 01, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a>, <a href=\"/Evaluation_Hash_Table\" title=\"Evaluation Hash Table\">Evaluation Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75\">Neural networks for Spanish checkers and beyond</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Game-AI Forum</a>, January 01, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=87\">AlphaGo</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Game-AI Forum</a>, January 29, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=AlphaGo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"AlphaGo (page does not exist)\">AlphaGo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60194\">LMR problems</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 16, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65365\">Unordered moves phenomenon</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66302\">Is chess still 99% tactics?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Tactics\" title=\"Tactics\">Tactics</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ajpc66\">Alvaro Cardoso - YouTube</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Profound\"></span>Apresentação de Profound, software para jogar damas classicas, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video </li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/z9iXnJppDX0?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alvaro_Cardoso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://checkers.fandom.com/wiki/Jogo_de_Damas_Cl%C3%A1ssicas\">Jogo de Damas Clássicas - Checkers &amp; Draughts Wiki</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=492099\">Re: Board Representation. Any strong chess engine uses this method?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2006</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_Guerra&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"João Guerra (page does not exist)\">João Guerra</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Classical Checkers</i>. Masters thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technical_University_of_Lisbon\">Technical University of Lisbon</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dspace.ist.utl.pt/bitstream/2295/1051359/1/dissertacao.pdf\">pdf</a>, pp. 5</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://damasclasicas.blogspot.com/\">Programas de Damas Clásicas</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Galician_language\">Galician</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Ren_Wu\" title=\"Ren Wu\">Ren Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Don_Beal\" title=\"Don Beal\">Don Beal</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ilk.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content24-3.htm#FAST\">Fast, Memory-efficient Retrograde Algorithms</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#24_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 24, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301151601\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nC